A man has sustained serious injuries when his vehicle crashed into the back of a truck on the R21 near the Benoni off ramp on Saturday.Upon arrival at the scene, paramedics found the vehicle almost completely wedged underneath the rear of the truck.&#8220;Paramedics could barely gain access to him but managed to treat him until he could be removed from the wreckage. Once freed, he was re-assessed and treated for his injuries before paramedics rushed him to Tembisa Hospital,&#8221; said ER24 spokesperson Werner VermaakParamedics explained that it took almost three hours to free the man from the wreckage.The cause of the crash is not yet known.-TNA Reporter 